                        <property name="label" translatable="yes">&lt;b&gt;What a check/dice role does:&lt;/b&gt;
- roles the required number of dice with the help of a random
  number generator (see below)
- consider custom dificulty or advantage (-/+)
- consider pain level

It does not:
- consider if you have enough Astral Energy Points
- consider if you have enough health points
- things I forgot to implement ;)

&lt;b&gt;Dice roles and random numbers:&lt;/b&gt;
